title: A Deep Dive Into Markets
itunes:title: A Deep Dive Into Markets
description:
Brett Ewing, Chief Market Strategist for First Franklin Financial Services, discusses markets and the Fed. Priya Misra, Managing Director and Global Head of Rates Strategy at TD Securities, talks rates and markets. Alan Rechtschaffen, Financial Advisor & Senior Portfolio Manager for UBS Financial Services, shares his investment outlook. Louis Navellier, Chairman, Founder, and CIO of Navellier & Associates, gives his outlook on markets. Hosted by Paul Sweeney and Kailey Leinz.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
